Doubts,' right; PHOTO: Robert Guillaume and Richard Libertini are uneasy
partners in 'Pacific Station,' far right; PHOTO: Ella Joyce and Charles Dutton
in 'Roc.'; PHOTO: Ashlee Levitch, Jeremy London, Sam Waterston, John Aaron
Bennett, Regina Taylor, 'I'll Fly Away'; PHOTO: Margaret Whitton, Teri Garr,
'Good and Evil.'; PHOTO: Harry O'Reilly and Sammi Davis-Voss share the best
years of their lives in 'Homefront'; PHOTO: Dabney Coleman is irascible again
in 'Drexell's Class.'; PHOTO: French Tickner and Michael Chiklis in 'The
